{"tag":"section","attrib":{"id":"idab403b0a-3a6f-11f1-a58a-d8db54b14ab5","identifier":"/us/usc/t10/s8687"},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"num","attrib":{"value":"8687"},"text":"§ 8687.","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"heading","attrib":{},"text":" Status of Government rights in the designs of vessels, boats, and craft, and components thereof","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"subsection","attrib":{"id":"idab403b0b-3a6f-11f1-a58a-d8db54b14ab5","identifier":"/us/usc/t10/s8687/a"},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"num","attrib":{"value":"a"},"text":"(a)","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"heading","attrib":{},"text":" ","children":[{"tag":"inline","attrib":{},"text":"In General","children":[],"tail":".—"}],"tail":null},{"tag":"chapeau","attrib":{},"text":"Government rights in the design of a vessel, boat, or craft, and its components, including the hull, decks, superstructure, and all shipboard equipment and systems, shall be determined solely as follows:","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"paragraph","attrib":{"id":"idab403b0c-3a6f-11f1-a58a-d8db54b14ab5","identifier":"/us/usc/t10/s8687/a/1"},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"num","attrib":{"value":"1"},"text":"(1)","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"content","attrib":{},"text":" In the case of a vessel, boat, craft, or component procured through a contract, in accordance with the provisions of subchapter I of chapter 275 of this title.","children":[],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"paragraph","attrib":{"id":"idab403b0d-3a6f-11f1-a58a-d8db54b14ab5","identifier":"/us/usc/t10/s8687/a/2"},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"num","attrib":{"value":"2"},"text":"(2)","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"content","attrib":{},"text":" In the case of a vessel, boat, craft, or component procured through an instrument not governed by subchapter I of chapter 275 of this title, by the terms of the instrument (other than a contract) under which the design for such vessel, boat, craft, or component, as applicable, was developed for the Government.","children":[],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"subsection","attrib":{"id":"idab403b0e-3a6f-11f1-a58a-d8db54b14ab5","identifier":"/us/usc/t10/s8687/b"},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"num","attrib":{"value":"b"},"text":"(b)","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"heading","attrib":{},"text":" ","children":[{"tag":"inline","attrib":{},"text":"Construction of Superseding Authorities","children":[],"tail":".—"}],"tail":null},{"tag":"content","attrib":{},"text":"This section may be modified or superseded by a provision of statute only if such provision expressly refers to this section in modifying or superseding this section.","children":[],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"sourceCredit","attrib":{"id":"idab403b0f-3a6f-11f1-a58a-d8db54b14ab5"},"text":"(Added ","children":[{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/pl/110/417"},"text":"Pub. L. 110–417","children":[],"tail":", [div. A], title VIII, § 825(a), "},{"tag":"date","attrib":{"date":"2008-10-14"},"text":"Oct. 14, 2008","children":[],"tail":", "},{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/stat/122/4534"},"text":"122 Stat. 4534","children":[],"tail":", § 7317; renumbered § 8687, "},{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/pl/115/232/dA/tVIII/s807/d/2"},"text":"Pub. L. 115–232, div. A, title VIII, § 807(d)(2)","children":[],"tail":", "},{"tag":"date","attrib":{"date":"2018-08-13"},"text":"Aug. 13, 2018","children":[],"tail":", "},{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/stat/132/1836"},"text":"132 Stat. 1836","children":[],"tail":"; amended "},{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/pl/116/283/dA/tXVIII/s1833/p"},"text":"Pub. L. 116–283, div. A, title XVIII, § 1833(p)","children":[],"tail":", "},{"tag":"date","attrib":{"date":"2021-01-01"},"text":"Jan. 1, 2021","children":[],"tail":", "},{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/stat/134/4234"},"text":"134 Stat. 4234","children":[],"tail":".)"}],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"notes","attrib":{"type":"uscNote","id":"idab403b10-3a6f-11f1-a58a-d8db54b14ab5"},"text":"\n","children":[{"tag":"n